qa_question-15-question = Which Operating Systems SlimeVR is Compatible With?
qa_question-15-answer = SlimeVR is compatible with Windows 8, 8.1, 10, 11, Linux, MacOS X, Android and iPhone OS.

qa_question-16-question = Can SlimeVR Be Used With Quest 2/3 Standalone?
