qa_question-17-question = What's SlimeVR Tracker Extension?
qa_question-17-answer =
    SlimeVR Tracker Extension is a smaller tracker that connects to a Main Tracker via a wire. It uses Main Tracker's Wi-Fi connection, battery and processing power, so it can be smaller and cheaper than a full tracker, and it also doesn't require charging.

qa_question-18-question = How SlimeVR Connects To a PC?
qa_question-18-answer = SlimeVR Trackers connect to your local network via Wi-Fi and can connect to your PC on the same network. Your PC doesn't need to have a Wi-Fi connection, as long as it's connected to the same network as trackers.

qa_question-19-question = Do I Need Fast Internet For SlimeVR?
qa_question-19-answer = SlimeVR Trackers don't require internet and connect to your PC via local network.

qa_question-20-question = Do I Need Good Wi-Fi For SlimeVR?
qa_question-20-answer = SlimeVR Trackers don't require good Wi-Fi, but if your network is congested or has too many devices, you may experience connection issues or lags, so the experience may vary.

