qa_question-22-question = How Many SlimeVR Trackers Do I Need?
qa_question-22-answer = At the very least to track your legs you need 5 SlimeVR Trackers - one for chest, two for thighs, and two for ankles. This will give you hip and ankle tracking (3-point FBT) as well as knee tracking as a bonus.

qa_question-23-question = How Can I Use Additional SlimeVR Trackers?
qa_question-23-answer = You can use additional SlimeVR Trackers to track more body parts, for example, feet, arms or head; or to improve tracking precision by adding a hip tracker.

qa_question-24-question = How Do I Charge SlimeVR Trackers?
qa_question-24-answer = SlimeVR Trackers can be charged with any USB-C charging cable and any compatible USB charger.

