qa_question-28-question = Do I Need 2.4Ghz Wi-Fi?
qa_question-28-answer = Yes. SlimeVR Trackers can only connect to 2.4Ghz Wi-Fi 4 networks. Most modern Wi-Fi routers support dual-band operation where you can have both 2.4Ghz and 5Ghz devices on the same network, so you don't need to downgrade your wi-fi for SlimeVR.